node.text:
What a shot! Bull's eye!😎

Dreaming of the Wild West? Riding a horse, wearing a hat, and taking part in duels? Glad we have a game that helps to feel this vibe!

Download "Western Sniper"!💪🏻

#azurgameslive #azurgames #westernsniper

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Azur Interactive Games on July 30, 2021. May be an image of apple and outdoors.

node.text:
Look at the precision! In a few minutes, he’ll be able to pick up a whole apple pie!💙

It’s so nice to spend some time outside when it’s warm and sunny...☺️

Have you ever fired a slingshot? Was it good?

Try playing «Slingshot Smash»!

#azurgameslive #azurgames #slingshotsmash

node.text:
Look at this intense battle! 
Do you think you could win on the first try? Because it’s hard to focus when enemies are coming from everywhere😳

It’s time to test your strength! Download «HeadHunters» and find out how skillful you are💪🏻

#azurgameslive #azurgames #headhuntersio

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Azur Interactive Games on July 19, 2021. May be a cartoon.

node.text:
How many different creatures exist in nature! It seems impossible to remember them all🤯 
For example, there are more than 3,000 kinds of snakes! 

Do you know any snake species? Have you ever met one in the wild?🐍

#azurgameslive #azurgames #snakearena

Hey look! All the characters are terrific!😍

So hard to choose… Which one do you prefer?

Download «Axes» and find your perfect warrior!💙

#azurgameslive #azurgames #axesio

node.text:
What an interesting installation! Do you like art?💙

Modern creativity never ceases to amaze. It is so original and full of splendour! 

What do you think the artist put into this installation? What is its main purpose?🤔 

Share your ideas in the comments👇🏻

#azurgameslive #azurgames #bottlejump3d

The night. The water. The lantern light...

In order not to get ambushed by the enemy, one must keep a round-the-clock watch. Stay alert! What if someone decides to attack at night? Or if a man is overboard?😰
